quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  37,114,And We had blessed on Moses and Aaron
  37,115,"And We saved/rescued them (B) and their (B)`s nation from the grief/hardship and suffering, the great"
  37,116,"And We gave them victory, so they were, they, the defeators/conquerors"
  37,117,"And We gave/brought them (B) The Book , the clear/evident"
  37,118,"And We guided them (B) the road/way, the straight/direct"
  37,119,And We left on them (B) in the others/lasts
  37,120,Safety/security/greeting on Moses and Aaron
  37,121,"We (E), like that We reimburse the good doers"
  37,122,That they truly are from Our worshippers/slaves the believers
  37,123,And that Elias (is) from (E) the messengers
  37,124,"When he said to his nation: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  37,125,"Do you call an idol statue/master , and you leave the creator`s best"
  37,126,"God (is) your Lord, and your fathers`/forefathers` lord the first/beginners"
  37,127,"So they lied/denied/falsified him, so they truly are being made to be present/attend (E)"
  37,128,"Except God`s worshippers/slaves , the faithful/loyal/devoted"
  37,129,And We left on him in the others/lasts
  37,130,Safety/security/greeting on Elias
  37,131,"We, like that We reimburse the good doers"
  37,132,That he truly (is) from Our worshippers/slaves the believers
  37,133,And that truly Lot (was) from (E) the messengers
  37,134,When We saved/rescued him and his family/people all/all together
  37,135,Except old/weak (his wife was) in the remaining behind
  37,136,Then We destroyed the others/lasts
  37,137,"And that you, you pass (E) on them in the morning/day break"
  37,138,"And at the night, so do you not reason/understand/comprehend"